title.narrative: RECLAIM Sustainability-Honduras Coffee

description.narrative: This project aims to: -Guarantee a better position of coffee producers with an emphasis on women producers for the generation of cultural change and economic opportunities, which is scaled throughout the entire coffee value chain. -Improve the transparency and fair value distribution in the Honduran Coffee value chain through inclusive dialogue with multi-stakeholders and decision makers (CSOs, government agencies, producers organizations, traders, etc.), as well as the development and adoption of digital solutions that will record daily farm practices and transactions along the supply chain.. -Engage coffee producers to change norms and influence policy agenda related to transparency and fair value distributions.
